                <mxCell id="examples_text" value="Equipment Class: &#39;Reactor Unit&#39;&#xa;Equipment Class Property: &#39;Volume&#39; (value: {10 000 - 50 000}, unit: liters)&#xa;Equipment: &#39;Reactor 1&#39; (ID: R-01, Level: Work Unit)&#xa;Equipment Property: &#39;Volume&#39; = 30 000 (unit: liters)&#xa;&#xa;Equipment Capability Test Specification may be associated with Equipment Class, Equipment Class Property, Equipment, or Equipment Property.&#xa;&#xa;Composition Note: Deleting an Equipment Class requires deleting all its properties. Deleting an Equipment requires deleting all its properties. Enforce at application layer since TypeDB doesn&#39;t support native cascading deletes." style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=10;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;" parent="1" vertex="1">
